I"¨<h3 id="install-dependancies">Install dependancies</h3>

<ol>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/esp-rs/rust-build#risc-v-installation">Install for RISC-V</a>
    <div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code> rustup target add riscv32imc-unknown-none-elf
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Install Cargo <a href="https://github.com/esp-rs/esp-idf-template#install-cargo-sub-commands">sub-commands</a>
    <div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code> cargo install cargo-generate
 cargo install ldproxy
 cargo install espup
 cargo install espflash

 cargo install --list
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/esp-rs/esp-idf-template#generate-the-project">Generate the project</a>
    <div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code> cargo generate <span class="nt">--vcs</span> none <span class="nt">--git</span> https://github.com/esp-rs/esp-idf-template cargo
</code></pre></div>    </div>

    <p>Typical output:</p>
    <div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code> ðŸ¤·   Project Name: blinky-rust-esp32c3
 ðŸ”§   Destination: /Users/sayanee/Desktop/blinky-rust-esp32c3 ...
 ðŸ”§   project-name: blinky-rust-esp32c3 ...
 ðŸ”§   Generating template ...
 âœ” ðŸ¤·   STD support Â· true
